# Falak Project Rule

- Work within this repository only and keep changes scoped to the request.
- Do not revert or rewrite unrelated local changes.
- Prefer small, focused edits and verify with relevant checks before finishing.
- When committing, stage only files related to the requested task.
- `push` means push the current branch to `main` in `aldhubaib/falak`.
- If a push target is unclear, ask before pushing.
- Remote target for push: https://github.com/aldhubaib/falak
